<h2 id="design-for-the-extremes">Design for the extremes</h2>

<p>Of course you canâ€™t create personas and empathy maps for everyone in the class, and you also donâ€™t need to. Generally speaking, 3-5 will capture the majority of Learners, but you should be conscious of whatâ€™s best for your Learning Design project. Too few and youâ€™re probably generalizing the traits too much and losing out on valuable details. Too many and youâ€™re casting too wide a net, and you will lose the ability to produce an effective learning experience. Generally speaking, all Learners will fall somewhere on the spectrum between struggling to understand and struggling to stay engaged:</p>

